commit.message:
ensure zmq objects are mockable

turn EINVAL into AttributeError for write-only attributes

explicitly avoid sharing context instances across eventloop Context classes

default inheritance is to share, so that a custom Context can replace the global instance,
but don't do so for our eventloop instances
